def solution(n, k, a):
    buckets = []
    for i in range(n):
        buckets.append((a[i], i))
    buckets.sort(reverse=True)
    time = 0
    for i in range(n):
        time += buckets[i][0] * (k // buckets[i][0])
        k -= buckets[i][0] * (k // buckets[i][0])
    return time


if __name__ == "__main__":
    n, k = map(int, input().split())
    a = list(map(int, input().split()))
    print(solution(n, k, a))
